leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">639.99 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div><div class="my-0 text-center md:text-left"> <span class="text-sm font-bold line-through md:text-xs">$999.00</span><span class="text-base font-bold text-brand-green md:text-sm">节省 $359.01</span> </div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-3.fill.size_2000x1125.v1710531698.jpg" alt="产品图片" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-3.fill.size_800x450.v1710531698.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-3.fill.size_1400x788.v1710531698.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-3.fill.size_2000x1125.v1710531698.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：亚马逊提供的产品图片</span></div></div><h2>零目标雪人 1500X</h2><p><strong>非常适合：</strong>离网使用</p><p><a href="https://zdcs.link/ePre7?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Goal%20Zero%20Yeti%201500X&amp;short_url=ePre7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">Goal Zero Yeti 1500X 的</a>充电功率为 600 瓦，容量超过 1,500 瓦，如果您要远离墙壁插座一段时间，它是理想的选择。它可以产生足够的电量来运行露营车，如果您投资面板以获得全部输入，它可以在短短几个小时内充电。</p><p> 1500X 还可以集成到您的房屋中，因此它可以成为真正的家庭备用装置，它甚至可以为您汽车的交流发电机充电，因此您可以在旅行时为其充电，而无需将太阳能电池板绑在家里屋顶。它还具有极其坚固的外观，如果您生活在相对恶劣的条件下，但希望能够在外出时运行一小群小工具和电器，那么它是一个完美的选择。</p><p>导航界面有点令人困惑，但智能手机应用程序的可用性在这方面有所帮助。如果您经常脱离网络，那么这是您的最佳选择。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md py-4 shadow-xl"><div class="order-1 mx-auto md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:flex md:w-full md:grow md:flex-col"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left">零目标雪人 1500X </div><div class="mt-2 hidden md:flex md:grow md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">1,809.85 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>现在去购物</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-8.fill.size_245x140.v1710531698.png" alt="产品图片" width="245" height="140" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-2 mt-2 hidden w-64 md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:block"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-8.fill.size_245x140.v1710531698.png" alt="产品图片" width="245" height="140" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-5 w-full"><div class=" hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>现在去购物</span></div></div></div><div class="mx-2 mt-2 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">1,809.85 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-4.fill.size_2000x1125.v1710531698.jpg" alt="产品图片" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-4.fill.size_800x450.v1710531698.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-4.fill.size_1400x788.v1710531698.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-4.fill.size_2000x1125.v1710531698.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：亚马逊提供的产品图片</span></div></div><h2>EcoFlow Delta 2</h2><p><strong>非常适合：</strong>停电</p><p>如果您此生主要关心的是断电时会发生什么，那么<a href="https://zdcs.link/1X8rR?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=EcoFow%20Delta&amp;short_url=1X8rR&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">EcoFow Delta</a>是一个不错的选择。凭借 1000 瓦时的输出（ <a href="https://zdcs.link/q7Km7?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Delta%202%20Max&amp;short_url=q7Km7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">Delta 2 Max</a>型号提供 2000 瓦时），您将永远不需要再次点燃蜡烛，因为您将<a href="https://www.popsci.com/gear/ecoflow-delta-2-solar-generator-review/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="（在新窗口中打开）">有足够的电力</a>来照亮房屋并在使用期间运行许多电器。如果停电持续时间比预期长，它可以在阳光充足的情况下在几个小时内充电。</p><p>它很重（约 50 磅），因此您不会在野营旅行中拖着它到处走，但它的动力、快速充电时间以及易于挂接到家中的配电盘上（如果您安装了<a href="https://www.popularmechanics.com/adventure/reviews/a11855/home-generator-101-how-to-power-on-when-the-power-goes-out/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="（在新窗口中打开）">转换开关</a>）使它成为它的最佳选择。非常适合偶尔发生的紧急情况。此外，它还可以通过连接在一起的电池轻松扩展，如果需要，可以将功率输出增加到 3000 瓦时。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md py-4 shadow-xl"><div class="order-1 mx-auto md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:flex md:w-full md:grow md:flex-col"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left"> EcoFlow Delta 2 </div><div class="mt-2 hidden md:flex md:grow md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">649.00 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div><div class="my-0 text-center md:text-left"> <span class="text-sm font-bold line-through md:text-xs">$999.00</span><span class="text-base font-bold text-brand-green md:text-sm">节省 $350.00</span> </div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>获得优惠</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HS1FVGFH2M1ZHCZ9MTXRBHHN/images-9.fill.size_245x228.v1710531698.png" alt="产品图片" width="245" height="228" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-2 mt-2 hidden w-64 md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:block"><img cl